  {
    "hotel_id": "1709863",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/grid-inn/hotel/seoul-kr.html",
    "name": "GRID INN",
    "detail": "The Grid Inn is in a cool part of the city tucked away within a myriad of interesting laneways behind a busy thoroughfare and importantly for many, a 5mins walk from the subway. The staff are excellent, mostly 20something women who had lived/studied abroad and spoke great English; know where some good places for food and shopping are and if the weather is really bad, would even order in amazing Korean fried chicken for you! Rooms are small - typical of Korea and Japan - but very clean with up-to-date fixtures/amenities and finishes. Breakfast was interesting... you could have eggs anyway you want as long as they were fried! And for a coffee-obsessed city, it was disappointing they only offered percolated drip coffee despite an espresso machine being in the dining area. Apart from this quirk, the front of house staff really do make this one of the best places to stay in fabulous Seoul. ",
