    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/k-pop-hotel-seoul-station/hotel/seoul-kr.html",
    "name": "ZIYOLK Seoul Station",
    "detail": "The room is tiny (like any hotel in this price range in Seoul)... however, it's fabulously clean and comes with a window in every room. That's IMPORTANT... I stayed in Seoul hotels without a window and it's disasterous for me. The hotel is on top of a hill, and you need to push your luggage up that hill... it can be a little challenging for some, I think it should be fine for most. It has two washers, free coffee, filtered water, juice, refrigerator in room and in basement, two desktops, and tables... and even a cooking area. Wonderful hotel!",
